title: Rhett’s Encounter With A Wild Bear | Ear Biscuits Ep. 352
description:
What has been your favorite job? Do you believe in Big Foot? This week, Rhett tells you his latest trip to woods and why you should always lock your doors. Link breaks down his experience at the recent Kendrick Lamar concert and you’ll learn all about what Rhett and Link’s most traumatic car accident. Also, a very special guest stops by!
